AzureBlade smiled: Thank you! I simply modified the DNA as to become 
fully transmetal.

He looked around. The city was still scorched from the attack of the 
fury cannon. Something had to be done.

AzureBlade: Prowl, I am back online. We have to do something about the 
city. The decepticons are licking their wounds, but not forever. Also, 
I have evidence that the predacons have captured and reprogrammed a 
maximal.
